<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I believe you're correct that he wasn't involved in that incident, but not that it was a coincidence. I think it's implied that Eustace and his spork <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I believe you're correct that he wasn't involved in that incident, but not that it was a coincidence. I think it's implied that Eustace and his spork were responsible for there being so many one-eyed men in the area and that he took out the preacher's eye back when they were rival bootleggers... I suspect Eustace had a lot to do with the preacher getting out of that business.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
